Package org.ietf.nea.pa.serialize.reader.bytebuffer

IETF integrity measurement byte buffer readers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PaAttributeAssessmentResultValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement assessment result attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeAttributeRequestValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement attribute request attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeErrorInformationInvalidParamValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement invalid parameter error information compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeErrorInformationUnsupportedAttributeValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement unsupported attribute error information compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeErrorInformationUnsupportedVersionValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement unsupported version error information compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeErrorValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement error attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeFactoryDefaultPasswordEnabledValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement default password enabled status attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeForwardingEnabledValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement traffic forwarding status attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeHeaderReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement attribute header compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeInstalledPackagesValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement installed packages attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeNumericVersionValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement numeric version attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.

    Reader to parse an integrity measurement operational status attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.

    Reader to parse an integrity measurement port filter attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeProductInformationValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement product information attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeRemediationParameterStringValueReader

    PaAttributeRemediationParametersValueReader

    PaAttributeRemediationParameterUriValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement URI remediation parameter compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeStringVersionValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement string version attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaAttributeTestingValueReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement test attribute value compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaMessageHeaderReader
    Reader to parse an integrity measurement component message header compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaReader
    Reader to parse an entire integrity measurement component message compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
    PaReaderFactory
    Factory utility to create a reader, that can parse an entire integrity measurement component message compliant to RFC 5792 from a buffer of bytes to a Java object.
